extendedInfo.description: Tracks Volleyball In game Scores and a few team stats. Aces,Kills,Defensive Errors(DE), Service errors(SE), Attack Errors(AE), and Attacks or  (Attk)This is a beta Version Only.The app will save  past games as long as app is  running  once closed completely all data is lost for now. I will be working to save data forever in the future. If you wish to save data for later I recommend taking a screen shot at the end of each game.
